Key Match Events: Alek Thomas hit a walk-off home run in the eighth inning
Gabriel Moreno drove in two runs with an RBI single in the eighth inning
Paul Sewald recorded the save with a strikeout in the ninth inning
Post-Match Reflections: Diamondbacks manager Torey Lovullo emphasized maintaining focus and competitiveness in the series
Paul Sewald expressed satisfaction with his performance in the ninth inning
Miscellaneous Highlights: The game featured a combined 16 pitchers from both teams
